channel.title: Need Help Changing Ip Of A Client To Mine!
channel.description: Ok, I Have A Client That I Downloaded. I Can't Get My Friends Online, Using That Client. I Can't Find The Old IP. This Is Not My First Client. I Don't Know what To Do, Becuase I Have Alrdy Worked On It, I Don't Want To Leave It Behind. Please PM Me. I Do Not Check My Posts Very Often. If You Help Me, You Get Donator Status(If You Continue To Play). If Your Experienced, This Should Be Easy. Base Is Delta. Please Help!

item.title: Need Help Changing Ip Of A Client To Mine!
item.dc:creator: @52x32x52x1 52x32x52x1
item.description:
@52x32x52x1 wrote:

Ok well, It would be in GUI.java (In client folder) or server.java. Open up one or both and go Ctrl+f and look for “No-ip” or “servergame”. Then it will hopefully find the ip adress for you. If that doesnt work, tell me your source.

Off topic: First post ftw?
